Australia to New Guinea, Solomons, Gr. and Lesser Sundas
Breeds in Australia and in Moa in the Southwestern Islands. On migration or wintering in the Lesser Sunda Islands, Celebes, the Papuan region, Bismarck Archipelago and the Solomon Islands.
